groves_swallow_rock_falls.html\" target=\"_blank\">\n                     <img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/dg6smdedp/image/upload/v1770983974/mailers/img/groves_ohiopyle_recb9s.jpg\" alt=\"James C. Groves -  Ohiopyle Falls, Youghiogheny River\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;max-width: 240px;display: block;text-align: center;margin: 0 auto;border:0;\" width=\"300\" height=\"250\">\n                   </a>\n                   <a href=\"https://www.bedfordfineartgallery.com/james_c_groves_swallow_rock_falls.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: #333; text-decoration: none; display: block; font-size: 14px; padding-top: 10px;\">James C. Groves -  Ohiopyle Falls, Youghiogheny River </a>\n\n                 </td>\n\t\t\t\t   \t\n\t\t\t\t </tr>\n             </table>\n           </td>\n         </tr>\n\t\t   \n\t\t   <tr>\n           <td width=\"100%\" align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"#fff\" class=\"column\" style=\"padding: 32px 0px 0px 0px;\">\n             <table width=\"100%\" class=\"content\" style=\"border-spacing:0;font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;text-align:center;\" role=\"presentation\">\n               <tr>\n\t           <td width=\"33%\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding: 0px 10px;\">\n                     <a href=\"https://www.bedfordfineartgallery.com/james_c_groves_upper_georges_creek.html\" target=\"_blank\">\n                     <img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/dg6smdedp/image/upload/v1770983973/mailers/img/groves_creek4_ovklzh.jpg\" alt=\"James C. Groves (American) Upper Georges Creek\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;max-width: 240px;display: block;text-align: center;margin: 0 auto;border:0;\" width=\"300\" height=\"250\">\n                   </a>\n                 <a href=\"https://www.bedfordfineartgallery.com/james_c_groves_upper_georges_creek.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: #333; text-decoration: none; display: block; font-size: 14px; padding-top: 10px;\">James C. Groves -  Upper Georges Creek  </a>\n\t\n                 </td>\n       